txt.en: 'So -- you bested Ilzk√¢l, eh? His braggart nature finally got him killed.'
'Glothrok is fallen. Take his tribute to the master of Moria.'
'What is this devil'ry? My vision blurs...poison....'
'Igash, we are betrayed! I give my life in service to you!'
'My devoted is slain! His tribute is to be delivered to Mazog!'
'I assure you, worms, my death will not come as easily as his!'
